Package: lacunr
Type: Package
Title: Fast 3D Lacunarity for LiDAR Voxel Data
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2023-10-12
Authors@R: person("Elliott", "Smeds",
  email = "elliott.alfred93@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"),
  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1054-7491"))
URL: https://github.com/ElliottSmeds/lacunr
BugReports: https://github.com/ElliottSmeds/lacunr/issues
Description: Calculates lacunarity curves for 3D voxel data using a fast C++  
    implementation of the gliding-box algorithm. Gliding-box lacunarity can 
    be calculated using the traditional fixed-boundary algorithm or the 
    periodic-boundary algorithm introduced by Feagin et al 2006.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.10), data.table
Suggests: lidR
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo, RcppThread
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
